# Personal data — never commit
# (As of the read-from-backup design, personal files live in $SUNO_SKILL_BACKUP_DIR
# and shouldn't appear in references/ at all. These entries are a safety net in case
# legacy copies show up here during development or transition.)
references/user-profile.md
references/inspiration-library.md
references/notebook.md
references/touchstones.md
references/*_catalog.json
references/*_playlists.json
references/.backup-path

# macOS noise
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# Editor cruft
*.swp
*~
.vscode/
.idea/
